# Yarn

This project uses `yarn` (Yarn Berry) as its package manager. Never use `npm` or `pnpm`.

## Core Commands

- `yarn <script>` - Run package.json script
- `yarn add <package>` - Add dependency
- `yarn add -D <package>` - Add dev dependency
- `yarn install` - Install dependencies

## Workspaces

- `yarn workspace <name> <script>` - Run workspace script
- `yarn workspace <name> add <package>` - Add to workspace
